Titolo: The Secret of Bastow Manor

Anno: 1983

Descrizione: The Secret of Bastow Manor is a 1983 graphical adventure game for the Commodore VIC-20 and Commodore 64 home computers. The Commodore 64 version is formally titled The Secret of Bastow Manor 64.

The graphics were done using PETSCII characters and the game is written in BASIC.